/**
 * AIQ Adaptive Assessment Engine — tRPC Router (v2)
 *
 * Architecture:
 * - LLM-first: every question is generated by the adaptive engine using the user's
 *   role, seniority, sector, AI usage level, and current capability gap profile.
 * - Async pre-generation: after submitAnswer, the next item is generated in the
 *   background and stored in session_metadata_json.pendingNextItem. The next
 *   session query serves it instantly (zero perceived latency).
 * - One-time baseline: the first session is flagged as isBaseline in metadata.
 *   All subsequent sessions receive prior capability scores for calibration from Q1.
 * - Rich item types: scenario_critique / output_improvement / error_detection
 *   return an aiOutput block; data_interpretation returns a dataContext block.
 *   These are rendered with distinct visual treatments in the UI.
 * - Static items are kept as an emergency fallback only (never served in normal flow).
 */

